狗炸狗撞狗都無人會指責(無話唔係人果d唔出聲啊)，因為學生已經佔領左道德最高地，保衛校園，自衛還擊，皆因有畜牲想射殺學生打死學生。<br />\n<br />\n3)學術聖地 ~ 美國民主法案由下年先通過到最快一周內通過，證明係文明社會，大學係神聖不可侵犯既莊嚴聖地。死守聖地，香港人英勇之名響徹全球，文明國家必須聲援；縱然城破，狗隻拈污聖地之罪行，文明國家亦必然聲討。"},{"pid":"5484caa202bb53bdffe05920d7c36bc9fbbce8d8","tid":1720792,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b1a1982fd1174124e405e24139b671cdc529e0","tid":1720792,"uid":158889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1eadacda42fba3f28d1eade0428cb4a23a459cf","tid":1720792,"uid":124382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a378f73e25c6b83492fb3725df8e81f5aaed89de","tid":1720792,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:03:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>紅隧、吐露港、東鐵線樣樣都係打擊位<br />\n咁樣你都話係佔領2.0?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:23:45.000Z","msg":"我可唔可以話叫人死守嘅都係 mon post 狗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:29:43.000Z","msg":"死守？？？攻都未攻叫死守 真係打到黎咪撤囉 on9 仔"},{"pid":"75b08457c22ec83c456f375fe8a85b3879caf782","tid":1720792,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a378f73e25c6b83492fb3725df8e81f5aaed89de","tid":1720792,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:03:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>紅隧、吐露港、東鐵線樣樣都係打擊位<br />\n咁樣你都話係佔領2.0?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:29:53.000Z","msg":"認真講，入去既唔阻，但本身出面既建議唔洗入去，佢一攻我就係出面開花，夠膽咪攻"},{"pid":"cc6a62d1137c9c3eda009881d674b7d9df4168c8","tid":1720792,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:30:41.000Z","msg":"嗰啲